I partner with Braellar most of the time (his HPs are close to mine) and we have our stratagies in place to pass agro from him to me, but I have an understanding that my real usefullness comes in when we take on the mobs where I will use my Defensive Disc.<br>
<br>
In short, its sad that I am mostly needed for only 3 mins..........as a woman...why does that seem so familar?<br>
<br>
So I repeat my earlier statment.<br>
<br>
Give me a Taunt that works..and doesnt fail..and refreshes quicker..and let me do my job!.....hehe Knights have better things to do then Tank.<br>
<br>
